---
title: Beyond Meat® Samosa 'Pockets' with Mango Chutney and Fresh Salad
description: Earthy and spiceful Indian flavours come alive in this recipe! This meal is Inspired by a popular Indian street snack, the 'Samosa'.  Beyond Meat® is cooked with a fragrant spice mix, peas and potatoes. Tucked inside a pizza dough and baked until steaming and crispy.
